Module kivakit.data.formats.csv

Package com.telenav.kivakit.data.formats.csv

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CsvColumn<Type>
    A typesafe model of a CSV column that belongs to a CsvSchema and can convert values for the column between strings and objects.
    CsvLine
    A model of a line in a CSV (Comma Separated Variable) file.
    CsvPropertyFilter
    A PropertyFilter that uses a CsvSchema to filter methods and fields to those whose names match columns in the schema.
    CsvReader
    Parses a stream of CSV information.
    CsvSchema
    An ordered collection of CsvColumn objects, specifying the structure of a line in a CSV (Comma Separated Data) file.
    CsvWriter
    Writes CsvLines to a PrintWriter using a given CsvSchema.
    UnquotedCsvReader
    Parses a stream of simplified CSV information.
